    "text": "Atmospheric conditions will be favorable for afternoon thundershowers in most parts of the island from tomorrow (20th April). Showers or thundershowers will occur at several places in Western, Central, Sabaragamuwa, Uva, North-western, North-central and Southern provinces after 1.00 pm.",
